{"id": "art-141", "label": "Art. 141", "title": "Art. 141", "slug": "art-141", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:\nblack'>Art. 141 </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_635493646\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2219\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_635493646\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Consiliul de <span class=SpellE>administra&#355;ie</span>\nse <span class=SpellE>întrune&#351;te</span> cel <span class=SpellE>pu&#355;in</span>\no dat&#259; la 3 luni.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1953828679\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2218\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1953828679\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)<span class=SpellE>Pre&#351;edintele</span>\nconvoac&#259; consiliul de <span class=SpellE>administra&#355;ie</span>, <span\nclass=SpellE>stabile&#351;te</span> ordinea de zi, vegheaz&#259; asupra\ninform&#259;rii adecvate a membrilor consiliului cu privire la punctele aflate\npe ordinea de zi <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> prezideaz&#259; întrunirea.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1939340808\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2217\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1939340808\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)Consiliul de <span class=SpellE>administra&#355;ie</span>\neste, de asemenea, convocat la cererea motivat&#259; a cel <span class=SpellE>pu&#355;in</span>\n2 dintre membrii s&#259;i sau a directorului general. În acest caz, ordinea de\nzi este stabilit&#259; de c&#259;tre autorii cererii. <span class=SpellE>Pre&#351;edintele</span>\neste obligat s&#259; dea curs unei astfel de cereri.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_732398370\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2216\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_732398370\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(4)Convocarea pentru întrunirea consiliului de <span\nclass=SpellE>administra&#355;ie</span> va fi transmis&#259; administratorilor\ncu suficient timp înainte de data întrunirii, termenul putând fi stabilit prin\ndecizie a consiliului de <span class=SpellE>administra&#355;ie</span>.\nConvocarea va cuprinde data, locul unde se va <span class=SpellE>&#355;ine</span>\n<span class=SpellE>&#351;edin&#355;a</span> <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\nordinea de zi. Asupra punctelor care nu sunt prev&#259;zute pe ordinea de zi se\npot lua decizii doar în cazuri de <span class=SpellE>urgen&#355;&#259;</span>.\nActul constitutiv poate impune <span class=SpellE>condi&#355;ii</span> mai\nstricte cu privire la aspectele reglementate în prezentul alineat.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_845895546\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2215\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_845895546\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(5)La fiecare <span class=SpellE>&#351;edin&#355;&#259;</span>\nse va întocmi un proces-verbal, care va cuprinde numele <span class=SpellE>participan&#355;ilor</span>,\nordinea deliber&#259;rilor, deciziile luate, num&#259;rul de voturi întrunite <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> opiniile separate. Procesul-verbal este semnat de\nc&#259;tre <span class=SpellE>pre&#351;edintele</span> de <span class=SpellE>&#351;edin&#355;&#259;</span>\n<span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> de c&#259;tre cel <span class=SpellE>pu&#355;in</span>\nun alt administrator.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}